    <AbilityDef>
		<defName>ScarletDevil</defName>
		<label>红符「红色不夜城」</label>
        <abilityClass>merissu.Ability_ScarletDevil</abilityClass>
		<description>用和弹幕一样的什么东西来制造巨大的十字架的符卡。红色的灵气看起来如同在燃烧一般，不过那似乎并不是火。

极限火花是利用迷你八卦炉的火焰发动的,这招则是暗夜力量汇聚后的产物,据说如果盯着看的话就会两眼充血辗转难眠。

使用时需要消耗一层灵力,发动后放出烧尽周围一切的红色灵气。</description>
		<iconPath>Abilities/ScarletDevil</iconPath>
		<cooldownTicksRange>600</cooldownTicksRange>
		<displayOrder>200</displayOrder>
		<aiCanUse>true</aiCanUse>
		<targetRequired>false</targetRequired>
		<verbProperties>
			<verbClass>Verb_CastAbility</verbClass>
			<range>20</range>
			<warmupTime>0.5</warmupTime>
			<soundCast>spell</soundCast>
            <targetParams>
                <canTargetSelf>true</canTargetSelf>
            </targetParams>
		</verbProperties>
		<comps>
			<li Class="CompProperties_AbilityGiveHediff">
				<compClass>CompAbilityEffect_GiveHediff</compClass>
				<hediffDef>ScarletDevil</hediffDef>
				<onlyApplyToSelf>True</onlyApplyToSelf>
				<severity>1</severity>
				<replaceExisting>True</replaceExisting>
			</li>
		</comps>
	</AbilityDef>

